  "name": "RPlog_Battle_of_Teyr_Part_2",
  "title": "The Empire Strikes Teyr",
  "summary": "Vadim's Imperial task force, under Admiral Bejin, arrives over Teyr and demands the surrender of Admiral Harkenson's dissident fleet; Harkenson refuses. Fighter commander Dante leads a tight escort formation shepherding Liza Molokai's bomber wing toward the resistance's command Golan, while Captain Mirden's outnumbered Star Destroyer absorbs a brutal multi-ship beating, using tractor-rammed corvettes and debris to even the odds. Through wave after wave of bombing runs and savage fighter duels, both sides lose Star Destroyers, but the bombers finally collapse the command Golan's shields and destroy it, vaporizing Harkenson and shattering the rebel command structure. With their leadership gone and morale broken, a junior captain surrenders the remaining resistance forces, and Imperial stormtroopers board the survivors for shipment to ISB re-education, though the rebel leaders remain hidden in the Teyr Rift.",
